question.title: Request digital certificate?
question.description: To save paper, we will send your certificate of participation via email after the event.

question.title: Request Official Receipt?
question.description: If yes, please indicate the full name of the person or entity making the payment, together with the Tax Identification Number (TIN).

question.title: Questions for speakers
question.description: You can send in questions you have for our speakers. Please indicate if it's for a specific person or for the whole panel.

question.title: Facebook Username
question.description: We'll put your profile picture on the FFC site! Join the other superheroes!
